Description:
You arrive at some ruins with huge columns still standing, under them there are piles of gold and rare objects like you have never seen before.

Among all the treasures there is a large jade chest that catches your attention, the chest is locked and sealed with magic, it seems impossible to open unless you have the key.
DescriptionAction: So unless you have the key you settle for the rest of the treasure.
